"      Dolobid (BF, BJ, CI, CZ, ET, GH, GM, GN, KE, LR, MA, ML, MR, MU, MW, MX, NE, NG, PT, RU, SC, SD, SL, SN, TH, TN, TZ, UG, ZA, ZM, ZW);",
"     </li>",
